# shellcheck shell=bash
# Optional direnv integration: auto-enter the flake devShell on `cd` so the
# project toolchain (rust, just, shellcheck, yamllint, taplo, treefmt, …) is on
# PATH without a manual `nix develop`. Run `direnv allow` once; requires direnv
# + nix-direnv.
#
# This is a CONVENIENCE for working directly on superzej. superzej itself does
# NOT depend on it — sandboxed worktree panes get the devShell toolchain
# automatically via `[sandbox] inject_devshell` (see crates/superzej-core/src/devenv.rs).
use flake
